<div>
	<h1 class="LargeHeading">2014 Global Markets &ndash;<br>A Year in Review</h1>
	<p class="TextIntroCopy">2014 opened with prices close to the record highs that had been achieved in 2013. Excellent returns and output conditions, combined with relatively low input costs, stimulated milk output to a very significant degree for much of the year.</p>
</div>
